rows.name:
Talk with the captain at the entrance
of the Divine Beast battleship

rows.label: qst300406_msg0002
rows.name:
Jeweled Signet? I'm afraid
I don't know of it...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst300406_msg0003
rows.name:
We are busy preparing for departure.
I must ask you to leave.

rows.label: qst300406_msg0101
rows.name:
Even if you are with the Special Inquisitor,
I cannot approve of you entering and exiting
the Divine Beast battleship...[ML:Dash ]
